The quests are exciting. My little Taru is running his butt off trying to find bomb ash for Berlina so she can clear her chiminy (her step mom knew the secret and gave me the hint). Oh, and Berlina told me about her neighbor who is scared to go outside, so I found him cowered behind some boxes and I gave him a Queven  (or whatever) backshell so he can run around like a turtle!<br>
