ALSO<br>
<br>
The three nations, while friendly, are vying for more landspace. So you take part of conquests. As you run around and kill more critters in the name of your kingdom, your kingdom gains influence. And if you control the area you get crystals, which you use in your skill crafting.<br>
<br>
OH and you get your own Mog.<br>
<br>
This game is soooo much better than SWG. I just wish there were more spells <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Oh well <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
